{# twig template #}
{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block page_title %}{{ 'Clean Gutter Co' }}{% endblock %}

{% block page_content %}

    {% embed 'layouts/right-sidebar.html.twig' %}

        {% block layout_page_title %}
            {{ 'Do you have clogged or dirty gutters?' }}
        {% endblock %}

        {% block layout_main_content %}
            <div class="col-12">

                <h2>Hire Your Local Gutter Cleaning Experts</h2>

                <p>Trust your home's care to the best gutter cleaner in the business. We provide top-quality gutter cleaning services in Byron, Warner Robins, Fort Valley, Macon, and Perry.</p>

                <div class="mb-3">
                    {% include 'components/image-carousel.html.twig' %}
                </div>

                <p>The difference starts with <strong>how</strong> we clean gutters. We don't use ladders, like you might think. We don't want to risk damaging your home, or risk falling from your roof.</p>

                <p>We use a high-powered vacuum system to 'suck' the gobs of dirt and leaves out of your gutters. It's state-of-the-art technology, and is powerful enough to pull root systems out of your gutters. Yes - we've seen trees growing in gutters!</p>

                <p>We can even record our work, using a wireless HD camera. You can <a class="text-link" href="" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#vacuum-vid-modal">see the results</a> first-hand!
                </p>

                {# Call Now #}
                <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid bg-white">
                    <div class="container">
                        <p class="lead">Ready To Get Your Gutters Cleaned?<span class="mr-2 ml-2"></span><a class="btn btn-danger btn-md" href="#" role="button">Call Now</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p>This system allows us to work safely on the ground, and still deliver the quality cleaning you expect.</p>

                <p>We always flush your downspouts to make sure the gutters work when we're gone.</p>

                <p>After the job is done, we clean up and take the mess with us.</p>

                <h3 class="mt-3">Here's How It Works</h3>

                <div class="accordion w-100 mb-3" id="accordionExample">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
                            <button class="btn btn-link w-100 text-left" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-12">
                                        <p class="display-6 d-inline">
                                            <i class="fa fa-check text-danger"></i>
                                            &emsp;Schedule Your Quote
                                        </p>

                                        <div class="d-inline">
                                            <i class="float-right fas fa-caret-down fa-2x rotate-if-collapsed" style="line-height:50%"></i>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </button>
                        </div>

                        <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p>Fill out the short form on this page or call us at (478) 261-1140. If you use our online form, we'll call you to schedule your free quote.</p>
                                <p><a class="btn btn-danger btn-sm" href="tel:1-478-261-1140">Call Now</a></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
                            <button class="btn btn-link collapsed text-left w-100" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-12">
                                        <p class="display-6 d-inline">
                                            <i class="fa fa-check text-danger"></i>

                                            &emsp;A Pro Will Come to Your Home
                                        </p>

                                        <div class="d-inline">
                                            <i class="float-right fas fa-caret-down fa-2x rotate-if-collapsed" style="line-height:50%"></i>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p>Our gutter pro will come to your home to perform an inspection of your home's gutters, and provide you with free custom quote. You just need to tell him to get started!</p>
                                <p>We prefer not to provide quotes without inspecting the home. This helps us give you the best price we can.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
                            <button class="btn btn-link collapsed text-left w-100" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-12">
                                        <p class="display-6 d-inline">
                                            <i class="fa fa-check text-danger"></i>
                                            &emsp;Pay Your Bill Online or In-Person
                                        </p>
                                        <div class="d-inline">
                                            <i class="float-right fas fa-caret-down fa-2x rotate-if-collapsed" style="line-height:50%"></i>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p>We can accept payments online or right at your front door. We accept all major credit cards, cash, and personal checks.</p>
                                <p>We can also arrange to email you an invoice, which will contain a link you can use to pay online.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            
        {% endblock %}

        {% block layout_sbr %}
            {% include 'components/forms/quote-request.html.twig' %}
            <div class="w-100 mb-3"></div>
            {% include 'components/testimonials.html.twig' %}
        {% endblock %}

    {% endembed %}

    {% include 'components/modals/vacuum-video.html.twig' %}

{% endblock %}